node.text: Totally caught off guard!!! Wow!! What a beautiful surprise to kick off Valentine’s Day weekend!! My baby @roccstarmusic you did that! The violinist was romantic and playing my favorite love song that you made! The gifts, the flowers, the whole ambiance made me feel special! You even thought of Amani, thank you! ❤️ you! Off to Aspen!
